room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Escape" by Escape the Room Texas in Houston
review: We did The Agency a couple of years ago for my daughter's birthday. We came back again this year and tried the Jurassic Escape. This room was awesome and well worth it! You will not be disappointed!

room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Escape" by Escape the Room Texas in Houston
review: Great experience. A bit complex for three rooms to solve in such a short time but an extremely authentic and exhilarating experience.
